<template>
  <v-checkbox v-model="isCheckboxChecked" label="終日" />
</template>

<script>
export default {
  computed: {
    isCheckboxChecked: {
      get () {
        return this.$store.state.isCheckboxChecked
      },
      set (newValue) {
        this.$store.commit('updateCheckboxState', newValue)
      }
    }
  }
}
</script>
